summary: cyrus is really the most selfless and caring person in the universe and it astounds me. back when he still had the crush on...
body: cyrus is really the most selfless and caring person in the universe and it astounds me. back when he still had the crush on jonah and both buffy and andi knew, there wasn’t a single second where i’ve seen him being bitter about the fact that he obviously wasn’t going to be with him ever. he just took whatever he could from their friendship and made do, without ever acting passive-aggressive towards him or andi out of frustration. he was always supportive of him and andi and their respective crushes on one another, always listened to their rants about this or that, always made sure they had the support they needed. he was always an amazing friend to both of them. and i refuse to think he’s never felt jealous, or sad, or heartbroken, because those are just natural feelings anyone would feel (especially when put in his very peculiar position), but the thing is he never acted on said feelings??? he just examinated them and kept them in check, and actually he examinated them and kept them in check so much that he learnt to accept them for what they were without making a big deal out of it. and he would’ve had all the reasons to, and it would’ve made sense for him to do so, because he’s a teen and teens make big deals out of everything—heck, adults make big deals out of everything!!!! cyrus was allowed to freak out and get openly sad and frustrated and pissy!!! it would’ve been understandable!!!! but he never did. that shows so much depth, so much maturity on his part. he’s such a wonderful human being, and a perfect friend.
